But `E[X_{i+1} | F_i] = X_i`. Therefore, `E[X_{i+1}^2 | F_i] ≥ X_i^2 = ‖X_i‖^2`.

Therefore, `E[‖X_{i+1}‖^2 | F_i] ≥ ‖X_i‖^2`.

So, this gives us the submartingale property.

